        <p>Be sure to stop for views of the beautiful Bear Creek Falls along the highway, and definitely stop at the Idarado Mine loop parking area, from which you can walk up a tiny hill to enjoy incredible views over the historic abandoned <strong>Yankee Girl Mine</strong>, which is quite photogenic. From this parking area you can also view other abandoned mining structures.</p>
